{"name":"beUI","description":"The motion toolkit for React and Next.js.","site":"https://beui.dev","endpoints":{"llms":"https://beui.dev/llms.txt","index":"https://beui.dev/r","shadcn_registry":"https://beui.dev/r/registry.json","shadcn_item":"https://beui.dev/r/{slug}.json","directory_registry":"https://beui.dev/registry.json","directory_item":"https://beui.dev/{slug}.json","detail":"https://beui.dev/r/{slug}","raw":"https://beui.dev/r/{slug}/raw"},"categories":[{"slug":"motion","name":"Components","description":"Bespoke motion primitives with shadcn-compatible registry endpoints."},{"slug":"blocks","name":"Blocks","description":"Composed, product-ready widgets built from beUI motion primitives."}],"components":[{"slug":"tilt-card","name":"Tilt Card","description":"3D perspective tilt on hover with cursor-tracked glare.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tilt-card","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tilt-card/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/tilt-card"},{"slug":"button","name":"Button","description":"Spring-pressed Button plus StatefulButton (idle → loading → success / error) and MagneticButton.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/button","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/button/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/button"},{"slug":"marquee","name":"Marquee","description":"Infinite horizontal or vertical scroll with pause-on-hover.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/marquee","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/marquee/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/marquee"},{"slug":"tabs","name":"Tabs","description":"Pill, segment or underline tabs with a spring layoutId indicator.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tabs","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tabs/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/tabs"},{"slug":"switch","name":"Switch","description":"Toggle with a spring-driven thumb and press feedback.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/switch","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/switch/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/switch"},{"slug":"input","name":"Input","description":"Text input with label, left/right icons, error shake and success check draw.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/input","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/input/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/input"},{"slug":"select","name":"Select","description":"Composable select primitives whose panel bouncily unfolds out of the trigger and separates, plus a Morph variant where the trigger grows into the panel via shared layout.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/select","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/select/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/select"},{"slug":"checkbox","name":"Checkbox","description":"Form choice control with a draw-on checkmark, spring press feedback and indeterminate state support.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/checkbox","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/checkbox/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/checkbox"},{"slug":"radio","name":"Radio Group","description":"Single-select choice control with a gliding layoutId indicator dot and spring press feedback.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/radio","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/radio/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/radio"},{"slug":"bottom-sheet","name":"Bottom Sheet","description":"Vaul-inspired draggable bottom sheet with snap points, inertia and glass surface.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/bottom-sheet","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/bottom-sheet/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/bottom-sheet"},{"slug":"shared-layout-bg","name":"Shared Layout Background","description":"A pill that glides between hovered items via motion's shared layout, with blur enter/exit.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/shared-layout-bg","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/shared-layout-bg/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/shared-layout-bg"},{"slug":"dock","name":"Dock","description":"macOS-style dock with grouped actions and a gliding active pill.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/dock","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/dock/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/dock"},{"slug":"tooltip","name":"Tooltip","description":"Hover or focus tooltip with blur enter/exit and spring spawn.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tooltip","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/tooltip/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/tooltip"},{"slug":"morphing-modal","name":"Morphing Modal","description":"Family-app-style modal. A single panel that morphs its height as you navigate between inner views, with blur cross-fade on content.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/morphing-modal","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/morphing-modal/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/morphing-modal"},{"slug":"text-animation","name":"Text Animation","description":"Animated text primitives for reveal sequences, shimmer loading states and letter-cascade swaps.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/text-animation","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/text-animation/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/text-animation"},{"slug":"number","name":"Number Animation","description":"Animated number primitives for count-up values and rolling digit tickers.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/number","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/number/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/number"},{"slug":"animated-badge","name":"Animated Badge","description":"Status badge with animated state icons, pulse feedback and compact size variants.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/animated-badge","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/animated-badge/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/animated-badge"},{"slug":"action-swap","name":"Action Swap","description":"CTA button and slot primitives for swapping text and icons with blur motion.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/action-swap","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/action-swap/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/action-swap"},{"slug":"animated-toast-stack","name":"Animated Toast Stack","description":"Stacked toasts with status morphs, swipe dismissal, actions and layout-aware motion.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/animated-toast-stack","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/animated-toast-stack/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/animated-toast-stack"},{"slug":"theme-toggle","name":"Theme Toggle","description":"Theme toggle button with a full-page rectangle clip-path reveal via the View Transition API.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/theme-toggle","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/theme-toggle/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/theme-toggle"},{"slug":"bouncy-accordion","name":"Bouncy Accordion","description":"Single-open accordion with weighted spring layout, icon rows and reduced-motion-safe content reveals.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/bouncy-accordion","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/bouncy-accordion/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/bouncy-accordion"},{"slug":"drawer","name":"Drawer","description":"Side panel that slides in from the left or right with a spring, backdrop blur, body scroll lock and esc-to-close.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/drawer","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/drawer/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/drawer"},{"slug":"scroll-animation","name":"Scroll Animation","description":"Scroll-driven motion: a Lenis smooth-scroll provider and a reading-progress indicator that reads from it.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/scroll-animation","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/scroll-animation/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/scroll-animation"},{"slug":"range-slider","name":"Range Slider","description":"Range slider with tick dots and a bouncy vertical-bar thumb that glides between snapped steps; drag and keyboard control, reduced-motion safe.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/range-slider","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/range-slider/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/range-slider"},{"slug":"table","name":"Table","description":"Virtualized data table that stays smooth at 10k+ rows, with sortable headers, row selection, column resize and reorder, and a sticky header. Minimal, reduced-motion-safe motion.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/table","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/table/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/table"},{"slug":"shader-background","name":"Shader Background","description":"Canvas shader backgrounds (mesh gradient, grain, warp, waves, voronoi, dot orbit and more) with a single typed variant prop. Reduced-motion freezes animated variants.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/shader-background","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/shader-background/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/shader-background"},{"slug":"cylinder-carousel","name":"Cylinder Carousel","description":"A carousel whose items line the inside of a cylinder, receding into the center and growing toward the edges. Drag, scroll or arrow-key to roll it, with a springy glide and snap. Reduced-motion drops the glide.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/cylinder-carousel","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/cylinder-carousel/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/cylinder-carousel"},{"slug":"loader","name":"Loader","description":"Loading indicator with seventeen variants: spinner, dots, bars, dot-matrix, dither, morph, comet, scramble, metaballs, newton, helix, percent, and five terminal-style ascii spinners. Scales from one size prop, uses currentColor, and reduced-motion swaps every transform for a calm opacity pulse.","category":"motion","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/loader","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/loader/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/motion/loader"},{"slug":"swap","name":"Multi-chain Swap","description":"Cross-chain swap widget with chain + token selectors, morphing views, animated flip and quote.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/swap","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/swap/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/swap"},{"slug":"dynamic-island","name":"Dynamic Island","description":"iOS-style island pill that morphs between live activity views with bouncy shell resize and blur crossfades.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/dynamic-island","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/dynamic-island/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/dynamic-island"},{"slug":"command-palette","name":"Command Palette","description":"⌘K palette with fuzzy filter, spring-animated active row and glass surface.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/command-palette","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/command-palette/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/command-palette"},{"slug":"expandable-action-bar","name":"Expandable Action Bar","description":"Compact icon actions that expand into labeled controls on hover or focus with shared layout motion.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/expandable-action-bar","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/expandable-action-bar/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/expandable-action-bar"},{"slug":"overflow-actions","name":"Overflow Actions","description":"Connected pill rail for primary actions that springs open to reveal extra controls.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/overflow-actions","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/overflow-actions/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/overflow-actions"},{"slug":"expandable-tabs","name":"Expandable Tabs","description":"Icon tab bar where the active tab expands to a labelled pill, with a panel above that morphs height and slides content direction-aware on switch.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/expandable-tabs","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/expandable-tabs/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/expandable-tabs"},{"slug":"swipeable-list","name":"Swipeable List","description":"Mobile-style list rows that swipe left or right to reveal contextual action buttons.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/swipeable-list","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/swipeable-list/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/swipeable-list"},{"slug":"file-upload","name":"File Upload","description":"Drag-and-drop upload queue with progress rows, retry/remove actions and reduced-motion-safe state changes.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/file-upload","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/file-upload/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/file-upload"},{"slug":"prediction-market","name":"Prediction Market","description":"Prediction market trade ticket with buy/sell modes, outcome prices, rolling amount entry, quick add chips and trade states.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/prediction-market","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/prediction-market/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/prediction-market"},{"slug":"wallet-card","name":"Wallet Card","description":"Wallet overview card with an account switcher and search that morph open from their triggers, a cascading balance with a live change pill and privacy toggle, copy-address, and Send / Deposit / Swap / Buy actions.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://beui.dev/r/wallet-card","raw_url":"https://beui.dev/r/wallet-card/raw","page_url":"https://beui.dev/components/blocks/wallet-card"},{"slug":"otp-input","name":"OTP Input","description":"One-time-code input with a gliding focus ring, digits that roll in per slot, error shake and a success check draw.","category":"blocks","detail_url":"https://b